WEBVTT

00:00:00.359 --> 00:00:02.790
Good morning, family. Thank you for

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:06.030
joining me today. I told everyone

00:00:06.030 --> 00:00:06.040
that

00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:08.669
the Lord showed me in 2020 there

00:00:08.679 --> 00:00:10.950
was going to be a chicken shortage, and

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:13.070
that it would extend into turkeys and cattle. It

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.589
would

00:00:14.599 --> 00:00:16.310
start messing with the cattle;

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:17.830
this was a planned event that things

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:18.910
would take

00:00:18.920 --> 00:00:21.590
place and

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:25.150
cause shortages of certain poultry items.

00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:27.230
I even saw at Thanksgiving time that

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.310
there would eventually be shortages of turkeys.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:30.990
I don't know when, so you're

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.389
going to ask, 'Was it this year?'I don't know.

00:00:33.399 --> 00:00:36.510
All I know is I saw shortages of turkeys

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:37.750
and that there would not be enough

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:39.950
turkeys for everyone to have

00:00:39.950 --> 00:00:39.960
one

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:43.110
at Thanksgiving time one year, and

00:00:43.110 --> 00:00:43.120
it

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:44.670
would start with the

00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:47.189
chickens. We

00:00:47.199 --> 00:00:50.670
see them talking about the bird flu

00:00:50.680 --> 00:00:52.150
and all the things about the bird flu,

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:53.750
and they eliminated all these chickens.

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:54.869
Now they're saying there's an egg

00:00:54.879 --> 00:00:58.349
shortage and they're trying to corner

00:00:58.359 --> 00:01:00.869
the market with the eggs. I was

00:01:00.879 --> 00:01:03.790
telling you all that I saw that

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:08.030
back in 2020. I gave words to the

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:10.190
church people; I wasn't on YouTube

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:13.109
yet, but I was giving them to my

00:01:13.119 --> 00:01:15.429
friends on Facebook and warning people

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:19.350
about having

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:22.350
chickens. I was shown that in 2020,

00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:25.510
so I rushed out and bought 21

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:27.510
chickens.

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:32.990
I raised them, and man,

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.710
they're nasty. When

00:01:35.720 --> 00:01:37.990
nothing happened that year, I told my

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.429
wife, 'I believe I've missed the timing

00:01:40.439 --> 00:01:43.310
of this.'I know what the Lord showed

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:46.789
me concerning the chickens, but

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:48.389
there's a depth

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:50.550
perception when you're seeing over in the

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.709
spirit. A lot of times when you're

00:01:52.709 --> 00:01:52.719
seeing

00:01:52.719 --> 00:01:54.469
over, it looks like it's right in

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:55.510
front of your face like it's going to

00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:59.190
happen right now, and it's a couple of years

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:03.870
out. Well, it was 2020, 2021, 2022, 2023,

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:06.990
2024, and here we are in 2025. Of course,

00:02:06.990 --> 00:02:07.000
everyone

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:08.550
knows that; I don't need to

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:11.869
say it, but here we are in 2025 and

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:13.869
we're seeing it in the news. At the

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:16.030
beginning here in

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:17.830
February, they're talking about all

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:20.830
this stuff. I personally believe, from what

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:23.750
I was shown in the vision, that this

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:25.990
would be—unless we've prayed it and made

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:29.110
it

00:02:29.110 --> 00:02:29.120
decrease—because

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:31.949
we've had time to

00:02:31.959 --> 00:02:33.750
pray over this. But we're still seeing

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:36.550
the fruit of it, and the Lord showed me

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:38.190
that it would increase and be a

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:40.509
pretty significant event.

00:02:40.519 --> 00:02:42.509
That's why I bought so many

00:02:42.519 --> 00:02:44.550
chickens.

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:48.390
What was the other thing that

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.550
the Lord showed me at that time frame? He

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:55.030
showed me that there would be strikes on

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:58.630
Iran, and the Lord showed me the price of

00:02:58.640 --> 00:03:00.350
the barrel of oil

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:02.390
eventually would

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:06.550
skyrocket, going very high. I saw gas

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:08.910
lines like it was in the

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:12.949
1970s, and there were people lining up

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:15.470
everywhere. It would create

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:20.110
a major

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:23.589
economic uplift in oil, and we as

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:27.190
Americans would 'drill, baby,

00:03:27.190 --> 00:03:27.200
drill.'We

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:30.830
would see a major

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:35.270
explosion in oil growth in Israel and

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:36.910
other parts, and

00:03:36.920 --> 00:03:40.030
I saw a

00:03:40.040 --> 00:03:44.190
season of oil going very high.

00:03:44.200 --> 00:03:47.030
When this took place, I saw Saudi

00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:49.030
Arabia and other countries

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:51.190
getting involved in it; it

00:03:51.190 --> 00:03:51.200
was

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:54.030
about trying to manipulate the

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:56.550
Petro dollar.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.149
The Lord told me that they

00:03:58.159 --> 00:04:01.030
were going to try to create

00:04:01.030 --> 00:04:01.040
a

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:03.830
green

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:06.830
agenda—things

00:04:08.470 --> 00:04:08.480
were

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.990
more dark than that,

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:16.150
like tentacles

00:04:16.150 --> 00:04:16.160
on

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:18.590
an octopus.

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:21.069
It all had different meanings

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:23.189
of why people were

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:25.790
doing what they were going to do

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:28.070
out of greed.

00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:30.270
That's why

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:33.029
I thought I needed a Tesla. I went out

00:04:33.039 --> 00:04:35.310
and tried to find one, and at that

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:37.469
time Tesla was shooting up and it was

00:04:37.479 --> 00:04:39.070
hard to find them. Then the bottom

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.950
seemed to fall out, and

00:04:40.950 --> 00:04:40.960
the

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:43.710
Tesla Model Y fell

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:46.830
in value. I think it's interesting

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:48.950
when you're seeing in the

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:52.390
spirit and you're

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:55.230
putting your own intellect into what

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:57.110
you're seeing. You try to put a time

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:58.670
frame on it, and that's why it becomes

00:04:58.680 --> 00:05:01.310
dangerous because we see

00:05:01.320 --> 00:05:03.790
in part, folks, just like the Bible

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:06.550
says.

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:09.590
Now we're seeing what I believe we're

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.749
about to see: what the Lord showed me

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:15.790
five years ago in the news about

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:19.350
chickens, about the earthquakes in Italy,

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:22.629
about Trump saying they

00:05:22.629 --> 00:05:22.639
want to

00:05:22.639 --> 00:05:24.909
protect Israel. Let's see

00:05:24.919 --> 00:05:27.790
what happens with that. I've seen at the

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:30.629
beginning of this year major strikes

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:33.270
coming against Iran soon, and that it

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:37.430
would be a crippling of Iran's

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:39.670
economy like we've never seen before.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:43.309
They

00:05:43.319 --> 00:05:45.790
would be set back greatly with their

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:47.749
nuclear program. I was

00:05:47.749 --> 00:05:47.759
shown the

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:51.270
missile that I

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:52.990
saw in the spirit

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.110
back in December

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:55.120
or

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:58.510
January.

00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.029
People were so

00:06:00.039 --> 00:06:02.469
upset that I showed that missile,

00:06:02.469 --> 00:06:02.479
asking

00:06:02.479 --> 00:06:04.950
why I showed

00:06:04.950 --> 00:06:04.960
that. I was

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:06.830
just

00:06:06.830 --> 00:06:06.840
trying

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:08.629
to be real with folks, but I don't want

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:10.189
to put the United States in

00:06:10.199 --> 00:06:11.870
jeopardy.

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:18.629
Today's topic: I was

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:22.629
shown in 2020

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:27.670
another major event

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:30.629
that is in the news now, but the Lord

00:06:30.639 --> 00:06:35.670
said they will not see this asteroid

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:39.029
coming. The major word I've

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:41.990
been getting right now is

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.270
about

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:46.390
earthquakes, a great shaking to

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:49.110
awaken. I've

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:51.469
been seeing a ramping

00:06:51.479 --> 00:06:54.029
up of that in my spirit. If

00:06:54.029 --> 00:06:54.039
we

00:06:54.039 --> 00:06:57.670
go back to what I saw about the

00:06:57.680 --> 00:07:02.670
asteroid, I saw a major asteroid

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:06.230
flying over the United

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:10.510
States of America. It was so loud it

00:07:10.520 --> 00:07:13.990
shook the houses

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:17.430
like a violent earthquake but from

00:07:17.440 --> 00:07:20.670
the sky. It shook all the roofs of

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:22.830
the houses

00:07:22.830 --> 00:07:22.840
and

00:07:22.840 --> 00:07:25.950
broke the glass out of the

00:07:25.950 --> 00:07:25.960
homes.

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:28.629
It was so loud it was almost deafening;

00:07:28.639 --> 00:07:30.629
it sounded like

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:34.230
a massive amount of noise in

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.510
the

00:07:35.520 --> 00:07:38.830
sky. It was moving so

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:41.430
fast, like

00:07:41.430 --> 00:07:41.440
the

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:43.629
speed

00:07:43.639 --> 00:07:46.629
of sound times 100.

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:52.270
As it came through,

00:07:52.280 --> 00:07:54.309
it just broke everything. I was

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:56.270
standing outside and saw it move

00:07:56.280 --> 00:07:58.790
overhead, looking like a

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:00.430
massive

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:03.909
flaming ball of smoke and fire. It

00:08:03.919 --> 00:08:07.550
left a ginormous tail.

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:11.350
The Lord showed it

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:14.510
moving over America, and

00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:17.070
they were trying to shoot it down

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:20.909
with lasers because there was not a

00:08:20.919 --> 00:08:24.629
rocket or missile

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:28.230
fast enough to catch it. They hit it with

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:30.790
a

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:34.070
laser and

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:37.310
struck it in half. Part of it

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:39.990
disintegrated in the air,

00:08:39.990 --> 00:08:40.000
becoming

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:42.029
little

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:45.829
pieces. This laser came from

00:08:45.839 --> 00:08:47.670
what looked like

00:08:55.560 --> 00:08:57.590
the New

00:08:57.600 --> 00:09:01.150
Orleans or Alabama area.

00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:04.310
This was a military kind of

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:07.550
laser, set up either

00:09:07.550 --> 00:09:07.560
in

00:09:07.560 --> 00:09:10.990
a

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:12.590
station there or off a

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:14.910
battleship. I

00:09:14.910 --> 00:09:14.920
saw

00:09:14.920 --> 00:09:19.350
this laser hit

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:22.110
this massive rock,

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:26.269
split it in half, and it disintegrated

00:09:26.279 --> 00:09:28.910
in fragments.

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:31.750
It was still significant,

00:09:34.910 --> 00:09:34.920
though.

00:09:36.959 --> 00:09:39.710
When one part of that

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:43.030
rock struck down, it struck in the

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:46.230
Atlantic Ocean by San Juan, Puerto

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:49.630
Rico. It was so

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:53.550
massive that it caused a tsunami wave

00:09:53.560 --> 00:09:56.150
that covered all of the islands; they

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:59.590
were completely wiped out. It

00:09:59.590 --> 00:09:59.600
covered

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:02.470
the tallest skyscraper in

00:10:02.480 --> 00:10:05.269
Miami.

00:10:05.279 --> 00:10:09.110
The water came inland so fast

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:11.710
and so violently that there was not

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:13.990
enough time for people when they

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:16.949
heard it go overhead.

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:21.910
The wave came in within probably

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:24.910
30 minutes

00:10:24.920 --> 00:10:26.829
to

00:10:26.839 --> 00:10:29.030
an hour;

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:32.030
it wasn't enough time to evacuate

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:35.310
everybody away from the

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:38.310
waterline. I

00:10:38.310 --> 00:10:38.320
saw

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:41.190
hotels in Miami and Fort Lauderdale

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:45.430
completely destroyed by

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:48.430
the tsunami wave that went all the

00:10:48.440 --> 00:10:51.949
way up to Cape

00:10:51.949 --> 00:10:51.959
Hatteras.

00:10:51.959 --> 00:10:56.910
It came inland several miles.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:07.110
Not only did it affect America, it

00:11:07.110 --> 00:11:07.120
affected

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:10.790
Europe, but they had longer to prepare.

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:13.509
It was devastation to

00:11:13.519 --> 00:11:15.750
their property, but they knew what was

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:18.550
coming because it hit America so quick.

00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:20.910
They had more time in Africa and

00:11:20.910 --> 00:11:20.920
the European

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:24.310
coastline to get away from

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:26.990
the water's edge.

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:36.509
I saw major landmarks in

00:11:36.519 --> 00:11:39.710
England and all over Africa with

00:11:39.710 --> 00:11:39.720
massive

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:42.350
inland water. It wasn't as

00:11:42.360 --> 00:11:45.829
bad as the American area because the strike was so close,

00:11:48.990 --> 00:11:49.000
but

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:54.509
islands like St. Martin and St. Thomas

00:11:54.509 --> 00:11:54.519
were

00:11:54.519 --> 00:11:56.389
completely covered

00:11:56.399 --> 00:11:59.790
with water.

00:11:59.800 --> 00:12:02.710
Now

00:12:09.160 --> 00:12:13.350
we see this asteroid in the news, about

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:16.470
2032 or

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:16.480
2038,

00:12:16.480 --> 00:12:18.509
and it looks like it has a

00:12:18.519 --> 00:12:21.509
real good chance of hitting the

00:12:21.519 --> 00:12:24.790
planet.

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:27.590
But

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:29.870
what the Lord showed me

00:12:29.880 --> 00:12:33.110
was something they did not

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:35.230
see.

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:41.670
NASA is saying

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:43.430
maybe they could bump it

00:12:43.440 --> 00:12:46.110
with

00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:48.350
technology and

00:12:48.360 --> 00:12:51.389
steer it off course.

00:12:51.399 --> 00:12:54.990
What I have seen is that it is

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:56.949
not stopped; it

00:12:56.959 --> 00:13:00.910
hits. Is that Wormwood?

00:13:00.920 --> 00:13:02.189
I

00:13:02.199 --> 00:13:03.870
thought, 'Lord, did you show me

00:13:03.880 --> 00:13:06.470
Wormwood? Is this in

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:08.550
Revelation?'People

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:11.670
are saying that Tom Horn had a book warning about Apophis hitting in 2029. I don't know the date; all I know is that in the vision, it felt like it wasn't winter, fall, or summer, so it

00:13:11.670 --> 00:13:11.680
has to be spring.

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.910
Tom Horn

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:51.310
said that it

00:13:51.320 --> 00:13:54.150
was in April, so it goes with

00:13:54.160 --> 00:13:57.550
what I felt in the spirit.

00:13:59.959 --> 00:14:03.990
Is that the 2029

00:14:03.990 --> 00:14:04.000
Apophis?

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:07.710
I believe

00:14:07.720 --> 00:14:10.629
when the Lord speaks to me,

00:14:10.639 --> 00:14:13.150
like he did with New

00:14:13.160 --> 00:14:15.470
Orleans. Everybody asked if

00:14:15.470 --> 00:14:15.480
I saw

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:16.790
anything about

00:14:16.790 --> 00:14:16.800
the

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:18.430
Super Bowl; I didn't see anything about

00:14:18.430 --> 00:14:18.440
that.

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:20.590
I told you what I saw: to

00:14:20.600 --> 00:14:25.069
pray over New Orleans, Las Vegas, and

00:14:25.079 --> 00:14:27.189
Nashville. I've seen the dump

00:14:27.199 --> 00:14:28.790
trucks; I

00:14:28.800 --> 00:14:30.550
have no idea where they went, but I'm still praying over

00:14:30.550 --> 00:14:30.560
them.

00:14:30.560 --> 00:14:33.069
I

00:14:33.079 --> 00:14:34.910
believe what the Lord told me about a

00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:36.670
Red Dawn

00:14:36.680 --> 00:14:39.710
experience. I try to be very

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:41.670
careful with what I say because

00:14:50.600 --> 00:14:55.230
there are rats

